      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "channel_lead",
      "label": "Channel lead copy",
      "default": "<p>Every channel has its own pace, pressure points, and path to sale. <strong>Carrier programs don't move like off-price buys. Marketplace velocity doesn't move like a national retail reset. Dealer counters don't move like big-box planograms.</strong></p><p>Valor supports partners with channel-specific execution across assortment planning, packaging compliance, fulfillment, retail intelligence, API/EDI integration, and inventory visibility - keeping the right accessories ready for the channels that need them next.</p>"
    },
